1
00:00:00,200 --> 00:00:01,400
welcome back

2
00:00:01,800 --> 00:00:05,400
today we are going to start working on the LuV quests

3
00:00:05,733 --> 00:00:05,866
and

4
00:00:05,866 --> 00:00:07,633
the first thing we want to do

5
00:00:07,633 --> 00:00:10,600
is to finish working on our naquadah setup

6
00:00:11,066 --> 00:00:13,033
that requires a precision assembler

7
00:00:13,033 --> 00:00:14,400
so we craft a new one

8
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:17,000
since the last one had been repurposed

9
00:00:17,066 --> 00:00:19,100
but since we lack Redstone

10
00:00:19,100 --> 00:00:21,700
we shall make a new ore drilling rig first

11
00:00:21,700 --> 00:00:25,200
and to keep track of its progress from our base

12
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:26,900
we can use this new cover

13
00:00:27,066 --> 00:00:28,600
we now have 3 miners

14
00:00:28,600 --> 00:00:30,666
and they are all out of drilling fluid

15
00:00:30,666 --> 00:00:34,100
maybe we have throttled the flow too much last time

16
00:00:34,533 --> 00:00:36,700
and after increasing the flow

17
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:38,233
they are all working

18
00:00:38,600 --> 00:00:40,500
and after not much time

19
00:00:40,500 --> 00:00:42,833
we are ready to craft our new assembler

20
00:00:43,100 --> 00:00:44,633
and we also are reminded on

21
00:00:44,633 --> 00:00:48,066
why we were feeding so little drilling fluid to the miners

22
00:00:48,066 --> 00:00:51,500
our ore processing plant is not being fed enough power

23
00:00:51,700 --> 00:00:53,266
since we have no hurry

24
00:00:53,266 --> 00:00:55,733
we lower back the drilling fluid speed

25
00:00:55,933 --> 00:00:56,800
just kidding

26
00:00:56,800 --> 00:00:59,633
we upgrade our mineral processing plant

27
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:01,533
the other thing we need

28
00:01:01,533 --> 00:01:04,266
is some precise casings for our new assembler

29
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:06,733
but those require a material

30
00:01:06,733 --> 00:01:09,700
which has to be cooked at ZPM voltage

31
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:11,900
which as usual

32
00:01:11,900 --> 00:01:15,733
we will do by using two energy hatches of the previous tier

33
00:01:16,333 --> 00:01:17,066
however

34
00:01:17,066 --> 00:01:19,700
while this allow us to make the required material

35
00:01:19,700 --> 00:01:23,266
it is also going to use half of our current power production

36
00:01:23,266 --> 00:01:26,300
and our battery is quite empty already

37
00:01:26,666 --> 00:01:30,400
so we quickly add some more reactors to our vacuum setup

38
00:01:30,533 --> 00:01:32,200
which fixed the issue

39
00:01:32,433 --> 00:01:34,533
until more machines turned on

40
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:37,466
thus we also upgraded our fluid plant

41
00:01:37,466 --> 00:01:40,066
starting from upgrading our heat exchanger

42
00:01:40,066 --> 00:01:42,266
into a Whakawhiti Wera XL

43
00:01:42,300 --> 00:01:45,300
and with an extra large heat exchanger

44
00:01:45,333 --> 00:01:48,266
we also want to extra large turbine

45
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:50,200
with all that power

46
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:54,300
we can now run our volcanoes with two LuV energy hatches

47
00:01:54,666 --> 00:01:56,300
and to keep up with those

48
00:01:56,300 --> 00:01:58,866
we also got a mega vacuum freezer

49
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:03,233
that thing will cool 250 items at a time

50
00:02:03,233 --> 00:02:05,633
but it also eat that much more energy

51
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:08,300
thus causing huge power spikes

52
00:02:08,300 --> 00:02:11,100
that our battery can't alleviate easily

53
00:02:11,666 --> 00:02:14,433
and the main issue is that it has no capacity

54
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:17,100
to craft better capacitor elements

55
00:02:17,100 --> 00:02:18,533
we need naquadah alloy

56
00:02:18,733 --> 00:02:19,800
and to be cooked

57
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:24,033
we need even more naquadah enough for the coils of a whole EBF

58
00:02:24,700 --> 00:02:27,700
so it is finally time to complete the precision assembler

59
00:02:27,700 --> 00:02:31,033
with precise casings that we planned a long time ago

60
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,700
and with that

61
00:02:32,700 --> 00:02:35,066
we can now craft the neutron activator

62
00:02:35,066 --> 00:02:38,400
required to complete our naquadah processing plant

63
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:41,500
that machine does not require power

64
00:02:41,500 --> 00:02:46,233
but it must be kept at a specific neutron kinetic energy in order to work properly

65
00:02:46,533 --> 00:02:49,800
if we turn it on when outside of the recipe range

66
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:53,133
the ingredients will be turned into useless waste

67
00:02:53,900 --> 00:02:55,800
to regulate the kinetic energy

68
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,833
we can use neutron detectors

69
00:02:57,833 --> 00:02:59,233
neutron accelerators

70
00:02:59,233 --> 00:03:01,266
and machine controller covers

71
00:03:02,266 --> 00:03:05,266
based on how high we build our neutron activator

72
00:03:05,266 --> 00:03:08,000
and how powerful the neutron accelerator

73
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:11,933
it will take more or less time to reach the target kinetic energy

74
00:03:12,633 --> 00:03:13,866
once we get there

75
00:03:13,866 --> 00:03:16,500
we can start processing the naquadah

76
00:03:16,833 --> 00:03:21,100
and we must make sure the kinetic energy is kept in check by the covers

77
00:03:21,100 --> 00:03:24,666
if it goes too high the structure will explode

78
00:03:25,466 --> 00:03:28,133
but what we are actually getting is naquadahine

79
00:03:28,700 --> 00:03:32,466
that stuff can be easily converted into ingots or dusts

80
00:03:32,466 --> 00:03:34,466
but we want to keep it like that

81
00:03:34,466 --> 00:03:35,733
because in that form 

82
00:03:35,733 --> 00:03:38,300
it makes wafers 10 times faster

83
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:42,866
so we quickly make patterns for the three main naquadah forms

84
00:03:42,866 --> 00:03:45,833
and craft on demand the required version

85
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:48,233
and with all that naquadah

86
00:03:48,300 --> 00:03:49,900
we can upgrade our EBF

87
00:03:49,900 --> 00:03:52,833
so that we can craft some better batteries

88
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:55,733
and by swapping just two capacitors

89
00:03:55,733 --> 00:03:57,933
we have three times the capacity

90
00:03:58,333 --> 00:04:01,066
and now that our power issues are fixed

91
00:04:01,066 --> 00:04:03,133
we can move on to the next task

92
00:04:03,133 --> 00:04:05,100
crafting a fusion reactor

93
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:08,733
and just when we started working on the controller

94
00:04:08,733 --> 00:04:10,500
we faced our first issue

95
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:11,800
we lack indium

96
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,133
to get it

97
00:04:14,133 --> 00:04:17,233
we have only two ways that aren't too convoluted

98
00:04:17,900 --> 00:04:21,800
one is destroying more aluminum in the setup we already have

99
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:26,533
the other one is use the byproduct of naquadria processing

100
00:04:27,833 --> 00:04:30,633
since we have some of that stuff lying around

101
00:04:30,633 --> 00:04:33,466
we can work that to get some extra indium

102
00:04:34,433 --> 00:04:37,000
and that is one energy intensive job

103
00:04:37,866 --> 00:04:39,766
but it already gave us enough indium

104
00:04:39,766 --> 00:04:42,000
for the reactor control computer

105
00:04:43,233 --> 00:04:45,000
the next expensive thing we need

106
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:47,233
is some superconducting coils

107
00:04:48,066 --> 00:04:50,533
which are going to require more indium

108
00:04:51,666 --> 00:04:55,933
thus we shall have more ore mining rigs across multiple dimensions

109
00:04:55,933 --> 00:04:59,100
to mine minerals that contain traces of indium

110
00:05:00,466 --> 00:05:02,000
and of course

111
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:04,266
to keep up with all of those minerals

112
00:05:04,266 --> 00:05:07,800
we also want to upgrade our ore working facility

113
00:05:08,466 --> 00:05:11,700
which is now becoming a huge source of pollution

114
00:05:12,666 --> 00:05:15,333
the last component for our fusion reactor

115
00:05:15,333 --> 00:05:17,533
is LuV machine casings

116
00:05:18,666 --> 00:05:22,000
those are made entirely out of rhodium plated palladium

117
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:25,933
which has to be cooked inside an EBF using some noble gas

118
00:05:26,233 --> 00:05:28,533
but we run out of those gases

119
00:05:29,033 --> 00:05:32,266
the easiest one to make is are gone out of liquid air

120
00:05:32,266 --> 00:05:35,200
however out current setup is too slow

121
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:40,100
so we shall swap our two small vacuum freezers with a big one

122
00:05:40,100 --> 00:05:43,300
that will work 250 times faster

123
00:05:43,833 --> 00:05:45,833
and after some time

124
00:05:45,833 --> 00:05:48,633
we have finally completed our fusion reactor

125
00:05:49,066 --> 00:05:50,666
before we can use it

126
00:05:50,666 --> 00:05:56,300
we have to wait for its 16 energy hatches to slowly load up its internal energetic buffer

127
00:05:56,866 --> 00:06:00,933
each recipe requires a specific amount of energy to be started

128
00:06:01,633 --> 00:06:03,900
we are going to use this first reactor

129
00:06:03,900 --> 00:06:06,533
to constantly produce helium plasma

130
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:09,433
that stuff has a high energy density

131
00:06:09,433 --> 00:06:11,666
but requires a plasma generator

132
00:06:12,533 --> 00:06:13,433
to make it

133
00:06:13,433 --> 00:06:16,400
we need deuterium and either tritium or helium 3

134
00:06:17,500 --> 00:06:20,666
since helium 3 can be pumped from many planets

135
00:06:20,666 --> 00:06:22,100
we chose that option

136
00:06:22,700 --> 00:06:26,933
and we will want to use the highest tier of oil drilling rig

137
00:06:26,933 --> 00:06:29,500
which however need at least IV power

138
00:06:30,100 --> 00:06:32,500
and since our fuel is slowly depleting

139
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:34,933
we shall power that one with the plasma

140
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:38,000
but since we need its output for the plasma

141
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:41,233
we shall kick start the loop by using some tritium

142
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,433
to get it

143
00:06:42,433 --> 00:06:47,533
we manually centrifuge some deuterium from our new deuterium setup

144
00:06:48,066 --> 00:06:51,000
we are not making this a definitive way of making plasma

145
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:55,633
due to the awful production ratio of 16 hydrogen to 1 tritium

146
00:06:56,633 --> 00:07:00,466
it indeed took quite some time for this tritium to be ready

147
00:07:01,466 --> 00:07:04,700
and now we can hit our fusion reactor with a hammer

148
00:07:04,700 --> 00:07:05,833
to turn it on

149
00:07:05,833 --> 00:07:08,333
since there are no other power switches

150
00:07:09,466 --> 00:07:11,933
once the first plasma batch is done

151
00:07:11,933 --> 00:07:14,633
we also manually fuse some europium

152
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:18,133
we need it to craft the plasma generator

153
00:07:18,733 --> 00:07:20,466
now we can go to Mercury

154
00:07:20,466 --> 00:07:23,400
where we can easily locate some cheap helium 3

155
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:25,266
with our portable scanner

156
00:07:25,866 --> 00:07:28,133
we build the oil drilling rig structure

157
00:07:28,133 --> 00:07:31,900
and set up a transceiver to swap fluids with the fusion reactor

158
00:07:32,833 --> 00:07:35,100
and once everything is ready

159
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:36,433
we can turn it on

160
00:07:36,433 --> 00:07:37,700
and realize that

161
00:07:37,700 --> 00:07:41,200
once again we have forgotten something to finish our building

162
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:42,700
this time

163
00:07:42,700 --> 00:07:45,700
instead of flying all the way back to our base

164
00:07:45,700 --> 00:07:47,900
take the missing pipes and come back

165
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:51,100
we use a specter key to open a portal to a pocket of space

166
00:07:51,100 --> 00:07:53,133
where we have access to ae2

167
00:07:53,733 --> 00:07:55,866
while that does not look much different

168
00:07:55,866 --> 00:08:00,466
consider that it takes about one minute to do the same task with a rocket

169
00:08:01,033 --> 00:08:02,933
and now the pumping can begin

170
00:08:03,466 --> 00:08:06,600
and with our new reliable source of portable fuel

171
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:09,933
we can start expanding our drilling capabilities

172
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:14,833
meanwhile our ore processing plant is expanding its pollution cloud

173
00:08:14,833 --> 00:08:18,300
which is starting to make our green grass fall as sand

174
00:08:18,933 --> 00:08:22,266
so we shall try to at least improve some mufflers

175
00:08:22,933 --> 00:08:23,400
however

176
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:26,500
while those upgrades allowed us to gather the materials

177
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:29,033
required for a second fusion reactor

178
00:08:29,033 --> 00:08:32,066
we are also running out of power again

179
00:08:33,433 --> 00:08:35,066
to increase our production

180
00:08:35,066 --> 00:08:38,533
we could burn some of the plasma that we are already producing

181
00:08:38,533 --> 00:08:40,200
however right now

182
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:44,933
we have no access to generators that can convert the energy at a high enough rate

183
00:08:45,733 --> 00:08:49,500
even the multi block turbine is limited by its dynamo hatch

184
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:54,133
and the best we can craft only allows for 100 thousand EU per tick

185
00:08:55,866 --> 00:08:56,733
but I think that

186
00:08:56,733 --> 00:09:00,400
we could also look into some more imaginative power source

187
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:01,866
such as naquadah

188
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:04,433
that stuff comes in different forms

189
00:09:04,433 --> 00:09:07,066
and can also be used in many ways

190
00:09:08,133 --> 00:09:11,066
and I think the easiest way to extract its energy

191
00:09:11,066 --> 00:09:13,700
is to shove it inside some tungsten cells

192
00:09:13,700 --> 00:09:17,733
and then shove those inside our old vacuum cooled nuclear reactor

193
00:09:18,066 --> 00:09:20,266
it can be clustered in many ways

194
00:09:20,266 --> 00:09:24,000
but I think we shall go with the one with the highest energy density

195
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:25,100
however

196
00:09:25,100 --> 00:09:28,933
that thing is going to be quite complex to manage and quite interesting

197
00:09:28,933 --> 00:09:32,000
so I think it shall have its own dedicated episode

198
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:34,733
where we will be trying some crazy stuff

199
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:37,233
you can wait for the finished result

200
00:09:37,233 --> 00:09:39,533
or you come see the live streams

201
00:09:39,533 --> 00:09:41,566
to see the humiliating fails

202
00:09:41,566 --> 00:09:42,100
bye bye

203
00:00:00,200 --> 00:00:01,400
欢迎回来！

204
00:00:01,800 --> 00:00:05,400
今天我们开始进行 LuV 的任务

205
00:00:05,733 --> 00:00:05,866
并且

206
00:00:05,866 --> 00:00:07,633
我们要做的第一件事

207
00:00:07,633 --> 00:00:10,600
是完成硅岩处理

208
00:00:11,066 --> 00:00:13,033
这需要精密组装机

209
00:00:13,033 --> 00:00:14,400
所以我们先做个新的

210
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:17,000
因为上一个已经另有他用

211
00:00:17,066 --> 00:00:19,100
但因为我们缺少红石

212
00:00:19,100 --> 00:00:21,700
所以先来个采矿厂

213
00:00:21,700 --> 00:00:25,200
为了可以在基地监控它的进程

214
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:26,900
我们可以用这个新覆盖板

215
00:00:27,066 --> 00:00:28,600
我们现在有三个矿厂

216
00:00:28,600 --> 00:00:30,666
而且他们的钻井液都用完了

217
00:00:30,666 --> 00:00:34,100
也许我们上次节流控制过甚

218
00:00:34,533 --> 00:00:36,700
增加流量后

219
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:38,233
他们都运行良好

220
00:00:38,600 --> 00:00:40,500
过不了多久

221
00:00:40,500 --> 00:00:42,833
我们已准备好制作新精密组装机

222
00:00:43,100 --> 00:00:44,633
我们也发现了

223
00:00:44,633 --> 00:00:48,066
为什么给矿机这么少的钻井液

224
00:00:48,066 --> 00:00:51,500
我们的矿处系统供电不足

225
00:00:51,700 --> 00:00:53,266
反正我们也不着急

226
00:00:53,266 --> 00:00:55,733
将钻井液的流量调低回去吧

227
00:00:55,933 --> 00:00:56,800
开玩笑啦

228
00:00:56,800 --> 00:00:59,633
我们升级了矿处系统

229
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:01,533
我们要做的另一件事

230
00:01:01,533 --> 00:01:04,266
是为新组装机准备精密外壳

231
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:06,733
但它所需要的材料

232
00:01:06,733 --> 00:01:09,700
必须在 ZPM 电压下制作

233
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:11,900
像往常一样

234
00:01:11,900 --> 00:01:15,733
我们使用 LuV 能源仓升压

235
00:01:16,333 --> 00:01:17,066
然而

236
00:01:17,066 --> 00:01:19,700
虽然这样能烧炼所需的材料

237
00:01:19,700 --> 00:01:23,266
但它将吃掉我们一半的电力产能

238
00:01:23,266 --> 00:01:26,300
而我们的电容库已经空了

239
00:01:26,666 --> 00:01:30,400
所以我们快速添加更多的强冷核电

240
00:01:30,533 --> 00:01:32,200
这解决了燃眉之急

241
00:01:32,433 --> 00:01:34,533
但更多机器启动就无能为力

242
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:37,466
因此，我们也升级了流体反应堆

243
00:01:37,466 --> 00:01:40,066
从升级热交换器开始

244
00:01:40,066 --> 00:01:42,266
把它升级成超大热交换机

245
00:01:42,300 --> 00:01:45,300
由于有了超大热交换机

246
00:01:45,333 --> 00:01:48,266
升级涡轮也势在必行

247
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:50,200
有了这么充裕的电力

248
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:54,300
用两个 LuV 能源仓运行炽焰高炉不在话下

249
00:01:54,666 --> 00:01:56,300
为了跟上高炉的效率

250
00:01:56,300 --> 00:01:58,866
我们还做了个巨型真空冷冻机

251
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:03,233
它能一次性冷却 250 个物品

252
00:02:03,233 --> 00:02:05,633
但它也会消耗更多的能量

253
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:08,133
从而导致我们的电容库

254
00:02:08,133 --> 00:02:11,100
有些无法应对功率的巨大波动

255
00:02:11,666 --> 00:02:14,433
最主要问题是它容量太小

256
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:17,100
制作更好的电容

257
00:02:17,100 --> 00:02:18,533
我们需要硅岩合金

258
00:02:18,733 --> 00:02:19,800
而且想要获得它

259
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:24,033
我们需要更多的硅岩来做高炉线圈

260
00:02:24,700 --> 00:02:27,700
所以是时候完成精密组装机了

261
00:02:27,700 --> 00:02:31,033
用我们早就计划好的精密外壳

262
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,700
有了这个

263
00:02:32,700 --> 00:02:35,066
我们现在可以制造中子活化器了

264
00:02:35,066 --> 00:02:38,400
作为硅岩加工中的必需品

265
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:41,500
这台机器不需要电力

266
00:02:41,500 --> 00:02:46,233
但它必须保持在特定的中子动能才能正常工作

267
00:02:46,533 --> 00:02:49,800
如果我们在配方所需范围之外打开它

268
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:53,133
材料会变成废料

269
00:02:53,900 --> 00:02:55,800
想自动调节中子动能

270
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,833
我们可以用中子传感器

271
00:02:57,833 --> 00:02:59,233
中子加速器

272
00:02:59,233 --> 00:03:01,266
以及机器控制覆盖板

273
00:03:02,266 --> 00:03:05,266
根据中子活化器的高度

274
00:03:05,266 --> 00:03:08,000
以及中子加速器的威力

275
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:11,933
决定机器达到目标动能的时间

276
00:03:12,633 --> 00:03:13,866
一旦我们到了目标动能

277
00:03:13,866 --> 00:03:16,500
就可以开始处理硅岩了

278
00:03:16,833 --> 00:03:21,100
我们必须确保覆盖板可以控制动能水平

279
00:03:21,100 --> 00:03:24,666
如果动能太高，结构就会爆炸

280
00:03:25,466 --> 00:03:28,133
但我们实际上得到的是氧化硅岩粉

281
00:03:28,700 --> 00:03:32,466
那东西很容易变成锭或粉

282
00:03:32,466 --> 00:03:34,466
但我们想保持这样

283
00:03:34,466 --> 00:03:35,733
因为在那种形式下

284
00:03:35,733 --> 00:03:38,300
制作晶圆的速度可以翻 10 倍

285
00:03:38,600 --> 00:03:42,866
所以我们快速为三种主要的硅岩形态制作样板

286
00:03:42,866 --> 00:03:45,833
并按任务所需制作它们

287
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:48,233
有了这些硅岩

288
00:03:48,300 --> 00:03:49,900
我们可以升级高炉

289
00:03:49,900 --> 00:03:52,833
升级到更好的电容

290
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:55,733
通过升级两个电容

291
00:03:55,733 --> 00:03:57,933
我们就有了三倍的容量

292
00:03:58,333 --> 00:04:01,066
现在我们的电力问题解决了

293
00:04:01,066 --> 00:04:03,133
我们可以继续下一个任务

294
00:04:03,133 --> 00:04:05,100
制作聚变反应堆

295
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:08,733
正当我们要制作控制器时

296
00:04:08,733 --> 00:04:10,500
我们遇到了第一个问题

297
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:11,800
我们缺少铟

298
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,133
想得到它

299
00:04:14,133 --> 00:04:17,233
我们只有两种不太复杂的方法

300
00:04:17,900 --> 00:04:21,800
一是继续土法制铟

301
00:04:22,900 --> 00:04:26,533
另一个是使用超能硅岩的副产品

302
00:04:27,833 --> 00:04:30,633
正好我们有一些超能硅岩

303
00:04:30,633 --> 00:04:33,466
我们用它来获得一些额外的铟

304
00:04:34,433 --> 00:04:37,000
这是一项高耗能工作

305
00:04:37,866 --> 00:04:39,766
但它已经给了我们足够的铟

306
00:04:39,766 --> 00:04:42,000
来制作反应堆控制器

307
00:04:43,233 --> 00:04:45,000
下一个造价不菲的东西

308
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:47,233
是一些超导线圈

309
00:04:48,066 --> 00:04:50,533
这将需要更多的铟

310
00:04:51,666 --> 00:04:55,933
因此，我们做了更多跨维度的采矿厂

311
00:04:55,933 --> 00:04:59,100
开采含有微量铟的矿物

312
00:05:00,466 --> 00:05:02,000
当然还有

313
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:04,266
为了能跟上采矿速度

314
00:05:04,266 --> 00:05:07,800
我们升级了矿处设备

315
00:05:08,466 --> 00:05:11,700
而它正成为一个巨大的污染源

316
00:05:12,666 --> 00:05:15,333
聚变反应堆的最后一个部件

317
00:05:15,333 --> 00:05:17,533
是 LuV 机器外壳

318
00:05:18,666 --> 00:05:22,000
它们是由镀铑钯制成的

319
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:25,933
通过在高炉中使用惰性气体制作

320
00:05:26,233 --> 00:05:28,533
但是我们的稀有气体用完了

321
00:05:29,033 --> 00:05:32,266
最简单的方法是使用液态空气

322
00:05:32,266 --> 00:05:35,200
但是我们现在的产能太低

323
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:40,100
所以我们将两个小冰箱换成一个大冰箱

324
00:05:40,100 --> 00:05:43,300
这是 250 倍的效率提升

325
00:05:43,833 --> 00:05:45,833
一段时间后

326
00:05:45,833 --> 00:05:48,633
我们终于完成了聚变反应堆

327
00:05:49,066 --> 00:05:50,666
在可以使用它之前

328
00:05:50,666 --> 00:05:56,300
我们必须等待 16 个能源仓慢慢缓存能量

329
00:05:56,866 --> 00:06:00,933
每个配方都有特定的启动能量阈值

330
00:06:01,633 --> 00:06:03,900
我们将使用第一个反应堆

331
00:06:03,900 --> 00:06:06,533
不断产生氦等离子体

332
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:09,433
那东西能量密度很高

333
00:06:09,433 --> 00:06:11,666
但需要等离子发电机

334
00:06:12,533 --> 00:06:13,433
要制作氦等离子体

335
00:06:13,433 --> 00:06:16,400
我们需要氘和氚或氦-3

336
00:06:17,500 --> 00:06:20,666
因为氦-3可以从很多星球上抽取

337
00:06:20,666 --> 00:06:22,100
就是它了

338
00:06:22,700 --> 00:06:26,933
我们要用最高级的油气钻井

339
00:06:26,933 --> 00:06:29,500
然而，它至少需要 IV 级电源

340
00:06:30,100 --> 00:06:32,500
由于我们的化石燃料正在慢慢耗尽

341
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:34,933
我们将用等离子为钻机供电

342
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:38,000
但既然造等离子体需要它的输出物

343
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:41,233
我们先用氚来启动循环

344
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:42,433
为了得到它

345
00:06:42,433 --> 00:06:47,533
我们从新的氘产线中手动离心一些氘

346
00:06:48,066 --> 00:06:51,000
我们没有把它作为制造等离子的最终方法

347
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:55,633
因为 16: 1 的恐怖产率实在难以承受

348
00:06:56,633 --> 00:07:00,466
氚元素确实花了不少时间才准备好

349
00:07:01,466 --> 00:07:04,700
现在我们可以用软锤

350
00:07:04,700 --> 00:07:05,833
来启动聚变反应堆了

351
00:07:05,833 --> 00:07:08,333
只因他没有启动按钮

352
00:07:09,466 --> 00:07:11,933
一旦第一批等离子体完成

353
00:07:11,933 --> 00:07:14,633
我们还手工聚变出一些铯

354
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:18,133
我们需要它来制造等离子发电机

355
00:07:18,733 --> 00:07:20,466
现在我们可以去水星了

356
00:07:20,466 --> 00:07:23,400
使用便携探矿仪

357
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:25,266
我们可以很轻松地找到氦-3

358
00:07:25,866 --> 00:07:28,133
我们放下油气钻井

359
00:07:28,133 --> 00:07:31,900
并配置空间传送器与核聚变反应堆交换流体

360
00:07:32,833 --> 00:07:35,100
一旦一切准备就绪

361
00:07:35,100 --> 00:07:36,433
我们将其启动

362
00:07:36,433 --> 00:07:37,700
又意识到一个问题

363
00:07:37,700 --> 00:07:41,200
我们忘带采矿管道了

364
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:42,700
这一次

365
00:07:42,700 --> 00:07:45,700
我们不直接飞回基地

366
00:07:45,700 --> 00:07:47,900
去拿我们遗落的管道

367
00:07:47,900 --> 00:07:51,100
我们用灵魂之匙打开空间传送门

368
00:07:51,100 --> 00:07:53,133
来访问 AE 网络

369
00:07:53,733 --> 00:07:55,866
虽然这看起来没什么不同

370
00:07:55,866 --> 00:08:00,466
但想想用火箭做同样的任务大约需要一分钟

371
00:08:01,033 --> 00:08:02,933
现在可以开始抽氦-3了

372
00:08:03,466 --> 00:08:06,600
有了新的可靠的便携式燃料来源

373
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:09,933
我们可以开始增强我们的钻井效能

374
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:14,833
与此同时，我们的矿处的污染有些难以遏制

375
00:08:14,833 --> 00:08:18,300
它开始让青草沙化

376
00:08:18,933 --> 00:08:22,266
所以我们至少要改进一些消声仓

377
00:08:22,933 --> 00:08:23,400
然而

378
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:26,500
虽然这些升级可以让我们

379
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:29,033
收集到第二个聚变反应堆所需的材料

380
00:08:29,033 --> 00:08:32,066
但我们电力又耗尽了

381
00:08:33,433 --> 00:08:35,066
为了增加发电量

382
00:08:35,066 --> 00:08:38,533
我们可以烧一些已经产生的等离子

383
00:08:38,533 --> 00:08:40,200
然而现在

384
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:44,933
我们做不了具有足够高能量转换速度的发电机

385
00:08:45,733 --> 00:08:49,500
即使是多方块涡轮也受到其动力仓的限制

386
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:54,133
我们能做的最好的动力仓只有 100 kEU/t

387
00:08:55,866 --> 00:08:56,733
但我认为

388
00:08:56,733 --> 00:09:00,400
我们还可以使用一些更有想象力的能源

389
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:01,866
比如硅岩发电

390
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:04,433
那东西有不同的形式

391
00:09:04,433 --> 00:09:07,066
能以各种方式使用

392
00:09:08,133 --> 00:09:11,066
我认为提取它能量的最简单方法

393
00:09:11,066 --> 00:09:13,700
是把它塞进钨单元里

394
00:09:13,700 --> 00:09:17,733
然后把它们塞进我们老式的强冷核电

395
00:09:18,066 --> 00:09:20,266
它可以以多种方式排布

396
00:09:20,266 --> 00:09:24,000
但我认为我们应该选择能量密度最高的那个

397
00:09:24,400 --> 00:09:25,100
然而

398
00:09:25,100 --> 00:09:28,933
那东西管理起来会很复杂，也很有趣。

399
00:09:28,933 --> 00:09:32,000
所以我认为它应该有自己专属的一集

400
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:34,733
我们将尝试一些疯狂的东西

401
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:37,233
你可以等待完成后的结果

402
00:09:37,233 --> 00:09:39,533
或者来看看我的直播

403
00:09:39,533 --> 00:09:41,566
看到一些耻辱的败北

404
00:09:41,566 --> 00:09:42,100
拜拜

405
00:00:25,200 --> 00:00:26,900
（数据发射器覆盖板）

406
00:01:40,066 --> 00:01:42,266
（我自己玩的时候一直没搞懂为什么是这机器名）

407
00:01:56,300 --> 00:01:58,866
（之后用巨冰箱/大冰箱指代它）

408
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:03,233
（准确来说是256）

